text: Welcome to 636 Fairway View Terrace, which lies within the highly sought after Timarron Golf Course community. All of this, located within the award-winning Carroll ISD, makes this home the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and modern updates, ready to welcome you home.

text: Discover timeless luxury & thoughtful design at 1006 Quail Run Road, a fully reimagined 9, 763 sqft estate situated on a beautifully treed 2.56 acre lot in the heart of Southlake's Quail Creek Estates. Originally built in 1987 & extensively renovated from 20212025 by the current owners in partnership with Bohanon Design Team, this 7-bed, 10-bath residence blends sophisticated & clean-lined architecture with top-tier infrastructure & finishes. From the moment you enter, youre greeted by natural light & sweeping views, thanks to 124 Anderson E-Series windows throughout. The home showcases a commissioned walnut-and-steel staircase & oversized kitchen island by Stahl Custom Lumber. The residence features 3.5 distinct kitchen & prep areas including a full main kitchen, an entertainment suite-MIL setup, outdoor kitchen & upstairs parlor. Interior highlights include 10ft ceilings, a Level 5 sheetrock finish, quartz window ledges, in-wall vacuum system with Hide-A-Hose tech, connections for 2 washer-dryer sets, hand-scraped white oak floors upstairs & finished concrete on the ground levelno carpet throughout. Cat-V wiring, Google Fire-Emissions detection & Savant media systems elevate everyday living, while sound-dampening insulation ensures privacy across all living & entertainment zones. Every detail was upgraded95% of wiring, all plumbing including a fire suppression system, four new HVAC units, foam encapsulation from roof to base & central steel beams designed to exceed 5x load requirements. The outdoor oasis is just as impressive. The backyard features a 45, 000-gallon, 10ft deep pool & spa with recently upgraded saltwater equipment, a custom Ipe diving dock, lush landscaping with mature oaks & Japanese maples & a turf athletic field with walking track & bleachers installed by the same professionals behind the Frisco Star. With no expense spared & no detail overlooked, this is truly a rare opportunity to own a contemporary, one-of-a-kind estate in Southlake, Texas.

text: Welcome to this stunning Bradford custom-built residence, nestled in the prestigious Timarron golf community of Southlake. Showcasing timeless Country French architecture, this elegant home seamlessly blends classic charm with modern conveniencejust minutes from premier shopping, dining, and entertainment at Southlake Town Square. Guests are greeted by an impressive Old World-style front door set in a protected alcove of Austin white stone and brick accents, leading into a warm and inviting two-story tiled foyer. Just off the entry, a private study features floor-to-ceiling bookcases, coffered ceilings, and glass French doorsan ideal space for remote work, a home office, or personal library. The open-concept floor plan is designed for both comfort and entertaining, with soaring ceilings, rich architectural detailing, and plantation shutters throughout. Natural light floods the gourmet kitchen, complete with granite countertops, a spacious island, custom built-in refrigerator, double ovens, and an adjoining wet barperfect for morning coffee or evening cocktails. Unwind year-round in the enclosed, tiled sunroom-patio that brings the outdoors in with serene views and natural light. The expansive primary suite offers a peaceful retreat, featuring a large walk-in closet, dual vanities, a luxurious garden tub, and a walk-in shower with built-in seating. Upstairs, oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets share a well-appointed Jack-and-Jill bath, providing both space and privacy for family or guests. The main-level laundry room includes a built-in sink and abundant cabinetry for storage and convenience. Step outside to lush landscaping and a private patioan ideal setting for grilling out or enjoying tranquil mornings and quiet evenings. Residents of Timarron enjoy an unmatched lifestyle with full access to HOA amenities, including a clubhouse, community pool, fitness center, greenbelts, jogging and biking paths, pickleball and tennis courts and a playground.

text: Located in Clariden Ranch on nearly three quarters of an acre, this stunning, fully renovated estate nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in Southlake has approximately $1 million in thoughtful, high-end upgrades blending timeless elegance with modern convenience and exceptional craftsmanship. Step inside to all-new wide plank hardwood flooring, freshly textured walls, and a completely repainted interior. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece featuring a True Residential fridge, Viking Tuscany dual-fuel range with double ovens, Miele and Bosch dishwashers, and a Scotsman nugget ice maker. Adjacent is a new wine bar and coffee station with two Sub-Zero refrigerators and a built-in Miele coffee system. Every bathroom has been remodeled, including a luxurious primary bath with a Kohler hydrotherapy spa tub. All new quartz countertops are found throughout, with Taj Mahal quartzite featured in the office along with a custom fireplace. Enjoy your own private theater with a Sony 4K projector, Marantz Dolby Atmos system, Klipsch speakers, and heated massage seatingall included. The smart home system offers voice-activated lighting, thermostats and security. Entertain in style with a new outdoor kitchen featuring a Lynx grill, stainless cabinetry, and granite countertops. Over 40 new windows, mahogany French doors & extensive landscaping complete the transformation. Additional features include 3 new high-SEER HVAC systems, epoxied garage with custom storage, and a fitness studio with iFit treadmill and Lululemon Mirror. Home offers school options to Northwest ISD Schools or Southlake Carroll Open Enrollment. Additionally, The Clariden School, a private International Baccalaureate School is located within the neighborhood.
